This function can be used to override the type-reference that this element exposes to the mapping system. This function must return an `ITypeReferenceData` object as follows:

```
{
    typeId: string;
    isNullable: boolean;
    isCollection: boolean;
    genericTypeId?: string;
    genericTypeParameters?: ITypeReferenceData[]
    }
```

